1、缩减命令：
 reduce the following to X words: （shift+回车）
复制的文字


2、增加命令
come up with a summary that is exactly x words:（shift+回车）
复制的文字

3、（直接命令）continue


 4、discuss the following results(就是把别的文章讨论部分复制过来)（shift+回车）
复制的文字（注意不要表格和图片，或者表格表达成有组织的段落）

5、（取一个好的标题使用这样的命令）suggest  a very eye catching research topic for the above
    (如果不满意，让它说更多) more suggestions

6、（因为这样的标题，让做出更多实验方法等）for the above topic ,create objectives and methodology of the paper

7、for the results discussion you made ,give recommendations and conslusion 

8、how many participants would you include to make the research valid in this case

9、come up with an introduction for the following research topic:  ......

10、write a retailed methodology for the above topic and introduction 

11、write objectives for this study

12、（引文的产生）先想出问题，搜索文章，找出相关度最的文章做引文，一个一个做就行了（semantic scholar）

